name: Free size Full mattress and box spring (Spenard)
description: It is a free mattress and box spring, size full. There aren't any weird, big stains on it. It is a little damp and has some easily removable nature stuff on it because it has been out on the patio for a few days, and one of the slats in the box spring is broken. But I'd sleep on it and it is free! You come and pick it up.
